        <obo:IAO_0000115>the mesectodermal cell layer arising from the trophectoderm that erodes the uterine mucosa and contributes to the formation of the placenta</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000412 rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon.owl"/>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000001>the mesectodermal cell layer arising from the trophectoderm that erodes the uterine mucosa and contributes to the formation of the placenta[MP]</obo:UBPROP_0000001>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000007>trophoblastic</obo:UBPROP_0000007>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000011>The postimplantation derivatives of the trophectoderm, which make up most of the fetal part of the placenta</obo:UBPROP_0000011>
