        <oboInOwl:inSubset rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon/core#pheno_slim"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Aggregate of cells forming the outer layer of a blastocyst, which provide nutrients to the embryo and develop into a large part of the placenta. They are formed during the first stage of pregnancy and are the first cells to differentiate from the fertilized egg. [Wikipedia:Trophoblast]</rdfs:comment>
