        <obo:UBPROP_0000007>buccal</obo:UBPROP_0000007>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000008>In many animals the inside of the cheek is lined with mucous membrane covered with stratified squamous epithelium and supplied with secretions from buccal glands.</obo:UBPROP_0000008>
