        <oboInOwl:inSubset rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon/core#vertebrate_core"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Rats do not have a gallbladder, but produce bile. The bile flows directly from the liver through the (hepatic) bile duct into the small intestine (Hebel and Stromberg, 1988)</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>gall bladder</rdfs:label>
