        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>the conducting airway of the lungs found terminal to the bronchi; these structures contain neither cartilage nor mucous-secreting glands; the epithelium of the bronchioles becomes thinner with each branching</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000412 rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon.owl"/>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000007>bronchiolar</obo:UBPROP_0000007>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000010>lacks submucosa and cartilage plates; they have 3 layers: mucosa, muscular layer and outer layer</obo:UBPROP_0000010>
