        <obo:UBPROP_0000001>An epithelium that lines the peritoneal cavity.[TAO]</obo:UBPROP_0000001>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000001>Serous membrane that forms the lining of the abdominal cavity or the coelom. It covers most of the intra-abdominal organs, supports the abdominal organs, and serves as a conduit for their blood and lymph vessels and nerves. It is composed of a layer of mesothelium.[AAO]</obo:UBPROP_0000001>
