        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>muscular tissue</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>portion of muscle tissue</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>textus muscularis</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
