        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The layer of glia and differentiating neurons that forms as a second layer around the germinal neuroepithium; as this develops it comes to lie between the ventricular and marginal layers and includes the basal and alar plates. Develops into neurons and glia forming a gray matter layer.</obo:IAO_0000115>
