        <obo:IAO_0000115>The distalmost portion of the digestive tract, derived from the hindgut, and terminating with the anus.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000232>this class is the superclass of &apos;rectum&apos;, which is currently reserved for the vertebrate structure. May be merged in future.</obo:IAO_0000232>
