            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The embryonic connective tissue made up of loosely aggregated mesenchymal cells, supported by interlaminar jelly, that gives rise to the developing cardiac structures</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000116>decide whether to merge with cardiac mesoderm. In EHDAA2 this lasts CS12-&gt;unbounded, includes mesenchyme of individual components as parts</obo:IAO_0000116>
