            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A division of the stomach. The stomach can be divided based on mucosal histology (glandular epithelium and gastric glands) and the relative position and type of gastric gland.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000116>We follow Kardong in defining stomach regions by gland, but we also include &apos;body of stomach&apos;. In future we may want to have different partitions of the stomach</obo:IAO_0000116>
        <obo:IAO_0000412 rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon.owl"/>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref rdf:resource="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stomach#Sections"/>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref rdf:resource="http://www.snomedbrowser.com/Codes/Details/245415005"/>
