        <obo:IAO_0000115>The aggregate of the coelemic cavity lumen plus the membranes that line the lumen.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000116>EHDAA2 distingsuishes between the lumen, the lining, and the &apos;coelomic cavity&apos;, which despire it&apos;s name, is not a space - it is the aggregate of space plus lining.</obo:IAO_0000116>
