        <obo:IAO_0000115>A subdivision of the autopod consisting of digit plus the region incorporating a single metapodial element. These segments are typically repeated along the pre-axiom to post-axial axis.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000232>this class represents a series of phalanges plus a metapodial element plus associated soft tissues. Instances of this class typically do not form a distinct unit.</obo:IAO_0000232>
